{"tid":833573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國大一新生「一輩子都不可能愛國」 入學資格被取消","createTime":"2018-09-23T15:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T17:40:37.000Z","uid":39464,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"10cdb7d84ea4c86a7ae3964ef12542fcbe35211e","tid":833573,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180923/large/1537680310_478c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180923%2Flarge%2F1537680310_478c.jpg&h=9c6f80b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n湖南城市學院一名大一新生(@微博「-貴州省省草王英俊」)辱華事件，近日有新進展，涉事新生的入學資格，已被校方取消。<br />\n<br />\n有關學院日前在學院官網發佈「關於取消土木院新生王棟入學資格的情況通報」稱，決定取消該學生入學資格。事源於本月19日，有網民曝光湖南城市學院土木工程系2018新生308班33號專門開微博發表「辱國」言論，微博簡介為「此賬號專注於乳滑（辱華）」。網上曝光的截圖顯示，微博為「-貴州省省草王英俊」發文稱，「如果真的少年娘則國涼的話，那我願意當娘炮」、「愛國是不可能愛國的，老子這輩子都不會愛國」、「軍訓到底有甚麼用，都大學了還想着給我洗腦」、「乳滑當然是要乳的，在這裏乳」、「都TM大學生了還愛國，我看你就是蠢貨」等等言論。<br />\n<br />\n19日，湖南城市學院在官網發布聲明回應稱，「-貴州省省草王英俊」為土木工程學院大一新生，學校正配合相關部門開展調查，並將根據調查嚴格依法依規處理。通報除了提及學生名叫王棟，更曝光其個人資料，引來爭議。通報還指，自9月9日入學以來，該學生多次在學生宿舍發表辱國言論，且不聽勸阻，並對同學愛國言論冷嘲熱諷，故校方決定取消他的入學資格。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180923/58714558\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180923%2F58714558&d=YiQ0ngMPxCLw3zTHWrzy77IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=ca571406\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180923%2F58714558&h=62ca9ecc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180923/58714558</a>"},{"pid":"fc38b39b80d8a3717a0a86839d1c35a09dfbabd6","tid":833573,"uid":199211,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:26:39.000Z","msg":"舉世皆濁我獨清<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 眾人皆醉我獨醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc1bb92a8e1b9137702b351ab4764bc09046f2f","tid":833573,"uid":75521,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T17:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21edc0d8e597890af56e31f38cc0fd624f06d29c","tid":833573,"uid":18955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T17:35:35.000Z","msg":"為申請政庇鋪路<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47777f8a7047c8bfccb8ccf672e8d7f0ffe76786","tid":833573,"uid":156069,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fc38b39b80d8a3717a0a86839d1c35a09dfbabd6","tid":833573,"uid":199211,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:26:39.000Z","msg":"舉世皆濁我獨清<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 眾人皆醉我獨醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T17:40:37.000Z","msg":"可惜現實是...他們醒我們醉..."}]}